00:02:30.585 --> 00:02:36.425
Scientology and Mormonism, they are inseparable from the men who created it.

00:02:37.115 --> 00:02:41.115
For starters, the lives of both founders, Joseph Smith Junior and

00:02:41.125 --> 00:02:45.415
L.Ron Hubbard have been greatly romanticised by their followers.

00:02:46.255 --> 00:02:51.235
Smith’s story is, as you will remember, of a young boy who is visited

00:02:51.265 --> 00:02:57.275
by God and Jesus, told where to find these mysterious golden plates, and

